
graph TD
    classDef plain fill:transparent,stroke:none,color:#000

    A[Real-Time Thermal Sensor Feed] --> B[Data Preprocessing]
    B --> |Frame Extraction| C[Time-Series Features]
    C --> D{Temporal Deep Learning Model}

    subgraph Model
        D --> E(LSTM / GRU Layer)
        E --> F(Dense Layer)
        F --> G(Sigmoid Activation)
    end

    G --> |Probability Output| H{Threshold Check}
    H --> |Exceeds Threshold| I[Proactive Early Warning]
    H --> |Below Threshold| J[Normal Operation]

    I --> K[System Shutdown / Cooling]

    C -.-> |Historical Data| L[Offline Training]
    L -.-> |Weights| D

    class A,B,C,D,E,F,G,H,I,J,K,L plain
